# Feature: Authentication

## Board Review

- **Product (Sarah)**: Approved - authentication is a core requirement for any user-facing app
- **Architecture (Marcus)**: Approved - OAuth2 + JWT is the industry standard. Stateless JWT keeps backend simple
- **Security (Aisha)**: Approved with conditions - must use PKCE for OAuth on mobile, rotate refresh tokens, store tokens securely (Keychain on iOS, EncryptedSharedPreferences/DataStore on Android)
- **Business (David)**: Approved - social login reduces signup friction, increases conversion
- **Decision**: Go

## Business Logic

